                        <h1><p>Combination solutions</p></h1>
                    
                </div>
                <div id="marketing_main_content_area_0_SubSectionDiv" class="sub-info">
                    
                    <div id="marketing_main_content_area_0_SubPriceDiv" class="product-price"><div>Multiple VELUX roof windows can give a room instant impact, maximising views and drawing in even more daylight.&nbsp;</div><div>By combining VELUX roof windows, homeowners can bring out the unique character of their property as well as&nbsp;</div><div>penetrating daylight further into their homes.</div><div><br /></div><div>For rooms to have adequate levels of daylight, it is recommended that the glazed area of all windows is no less than&nbsp;</div><div>20% of the floor area of the room. The range of combination solutions from VELUX can easily help to achieve this&nbsp;</div><div>recommended 20% glazed area.</div></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
