<!-- GlobalLocalHeadline.ascx -->

    
    <h2>Extend with sloping elements</h2>
     


	                    <div class="article-content clearfix">
							
    If the pitch of the roof continues to the floor, there is an option to extend a VELUX roof window by installing an additional fixed window element directly below. These windows have a fixed sash and cannot be opened. Additional sloping elements are available in a range of finishes GIL (white painted or clear lacquered pine wood) or GIU (white polyurethane, maintenance free) to match other roof window elements. Combining a roof window with a GIL/GIU provides significantly more natural light for homeowners seeking more daylight.&nbsp;
    


						</div>
					
				</div>
			
        
                <div class="button-wrapper">
                    
    
    
    
