<!-- GlobalLocalHeadline.ascx -->

    
    <h2>Extend with vertical elements</h2>
     


	                    <div class="article-content clearfix">
							
    Vertical window elements are designed to be installed directly below a VELUX standard roof window. As the windows stretch nearly all the way to the floor, they ensure a great outwards view for the occupant. Options include either a vertical window element VFE that opens inwards using a handle at the top of the sash or a fixed VIU that cannot be opened. Maintenance-free windows (VIU) do not require repainting, but can be cleaned with a soft, damp cloth if needed.
    


						</div>
					
				</div>
			
        
                <div class="button-wrapper">
                    
    
    
    
