    <h2>Horizontal duo solution</h2>
     


	                    <div class="article-content clearfix">
							
    An effective solution to invite in more daylight is to install two identical size VELUX roof windows side-by-side. Depending on the available space, choose between centre pivot or top-hung roof windows. Centre pivot roof windows have a unique control bar at the top, making them easy to operate even with furniture placed directly under the window. Top-hung roof windows offer panoramic views when fully opened and are ideally suited to lofts.&nbsp;<br />
<br />
    


						</div>
					
				</div>
			
        
