<!-- GlobalLocalHeadline.ascx -->

    
    <h2>Vertical duo solution</h2>
     


	                    <div class="article-content clearfix">
							
    Where space allows or where homeowners wish to make a statement, consider installing two identical size VELUX roof windows, one above the other, to create a light-filled room with the feeling of being outside. For ultimate comfort, or if these VELUX roof windows are out-of-reach, there is the option of upgrading to the remote-controlled VELUX INTEGRA&reg; roof windows.<br />
<br />
    


