    <h2>Quattro solution</h2>
     


	                    <div class="article-content clearfix">
							
    Four VELUX roof windows installed both above and beside each other offers a showstopping daylight solution to any room. The ultimate combination for homeowners to create a bright, welcoming, and desirable atmosphere. For added comfort or if roof windows are situated out-of-reach, remote-controlled VELUX INTEGRA&reg; roof windows can be integrated into this solution.<br />
